      • checkImmutability

      • checkDupFieldNames

        public void checkDupFieldNames(Program prog)
        Checks that no structures have duplicated field names. In particular, a field in a structure or filter can't have the same name as another field in the same structure or parent structure or filter. Also checks that no mutable structs are fields in an immutable struct.
        Parameters:
        prog - parsed program object to check
        streamNames - map from top-level stream and structure names to FEContexts in which they are defined

      • checkPackageNames

        public java.util.Map checkPackageNames(Program prog)
        Checks that the provided program does not have duplicate names of structures or streams.
        Parameters:
        prog - parsed program object to check
